*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /ˈɪdɪəm/
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /"IdI@m/

=== Noun ===
# an [[expression]] or [[phrase]] formed by two or more words which can usually not be fully understood from the separate meanings of the individual words which form it, but instead needs to be learned as a whole unit of meaning.
#: (e.g. ''get along'')
# a manner of speaking, a way of expressing one's self

